This is a remake of the Halo 3 map Crypt for GG/DM. Unfortunately i haven't had a chance to play it (in halo 3) so i had to build it based on a few pics... Specs:
40 spawns, buyzones, some brush-based props, a few traps, animated
Please visit Clan 5k3's studio for more Halo css maps and materials.
